      "title": "CEB warns over delays in restoring power outages due to fuel crisis",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ceylon Electricity Board (CEB) said there could be some delays in restoring the supply of electricity following outages due to fuel crisis.",
        "The CEB said it has to identify the priorities and direct the vehicles in the field service of the CEB for the restoration of power outages and maintenance work due to the lack of fuel.",
        "The CEB also said that it is committed to providing electricity as soon as possible to minimize the inconvenience to the consumers."
      ],
